</p><p>
Unlock the secrets of your super-powers!
</p><p>
<br/>
</p><p>
Everyone has a super-power.  It is that special ingredient that makes
you tick.  Each person is unique in how they think, how they act, and
the experiences that they have.  Discover how to use your unique
personal attributes to get the most from your life.
</p><p>
<b>Author</b>
</p><p>
Mark Seaman is an author, inventor, and software developer.  He has
spent a lifetime trying to understand complex systems.  His unique
vantage point on what makes systems work and how they break can also
be applied to people.
</p><p>
<img src="/media/mybook/images/Mark.Seaman.200.jpg" alt="Mark.Seaman.200.jpg">
</p><p>
Learn more at <a href="http://MarkSeaman.org/" target="_blank">http://MarkSeaman.org/</a>
</p><p>
</p><p>
<b>Shrinking World Guides</b>
</p><p>
</p><p>
Shrinking World Guides provide you with tips for how to thrive in the
modern world.  The focus of these articles is applying technologies to
simplify your life. Some small changes will make things a lot easier
for you. Here you will find pointers that help you use technology to
solve real-world problems.
</p><p>
A Shrinking World Guide is a web site, and online book dedicated to
Technology, Personal Effectiveness, and Leadership. These
important topics are interesting in their own right, but they are
also synergistic.
</p><p>
Learn more at <a href="http://shrinking-world.org" target="_blank">http://shrinking-world.org</a>
</p><p>
</p><p>
<b>Super-power Handbook</b>
</p><p>
Discover and develop your full potential.  Learn to cultivate the
talents and skills.  Maximize the most fulfilling experiences that
you have.  This book will step you through the process of evaluating
and optimizing the things that matter most in your life.
</p><p>

